{"tid":2053764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[高雄突發] 挺韓的國民黨高雄市議會議長許崑源晚上突墜樓身亡","createTime":"2020-06-06T14:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T14:53:24.000Z","uid":22556,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"76deba7c1984a4d25c9ead213095b1514adacbbd","tid":2053764,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T14:28:10.000Z","msg":"高雄市長韓國瑜確定被罷免，向來力挺韓國瑜的國民黨高雄市議會議長許崑源，剛剛傳出在高雄市四維路的住宅大樓墜樓，當場死亡。目前警方正封鎖現場進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n今天晚間9時許，高市議長許崑源驚傳在自家大樓跳樓身亡，警方獲報趕往現場，初步察看許崑源已無生命跡象，警方鑑識人員已趕往現場採證。<br />\n<br />\n稍早前，議會新聞群組還貼了一段許崑源議長對韓國瑜被罷免成功後的說法，許表示對市長罷免投票結果尊重，但強調，他也對市民失去認真改變高雄、努力讓高雄更好的市長，感到非常遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n許崑源說，感謝市府團隊在過去一年半的努力與打拼，高雄的進步不能停，期盼全體市民一起讓高雄愈來愈好。沒想到隨後卻傳來自殺的不幸消息。<br />\n（地方中心/高雄報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200606/M6OGKATJUZUT5OHRL5CN4WBBLM/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200606%2FM6OGKATJUZUT5OHRL5CN4WBBLM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx7XdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=56fa71b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200606%2FM6OGKATJUZUT5OHRL5CN4WBBLM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=96f9557e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200606/M6OGKATJUZUT5OHRL5CN4WBBLM/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"0f12d9d7e1a8181c0409a1105912307d223d7994","tid":2053764,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T14:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毛主席急召"},{"pid":"db82ff02abceb80585b99e8f04d